    "description": "<i>Unstoppable</i> is an adrenaline-pumping horror adventure where you’re tasked with escaping Schindler Tower.<br><br>A mysterious gas has turned office workers insane … Now everyone is out for blood. Face dimly-lit corridors filled with death, search for clues to find a cure, and keep the psychotic horde at bay any way you can. Will you get to the bottom of the infection or die in the dark?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/6684beecceb6b1a608e6d06ffd1a6939.webp?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/e090e5941a036012e7525a3c3c0ed2fd.poster.avif?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/e090e5941a036012e7525a3c3c0ed2fd.webm?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/e090e5941a036012e7525a3c3c0ed2fd.mp4?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Challenging, physics-based combat. Feel the weight of each blow and dodge infected enemies. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/984254e9bfb8a5a4af1689380abbbc32.webp?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/dcc432d5632ebd60cb90f6ed76ac2993.poster.avif?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/dcc432d5632ebd60cb90f6ed76ac2993.webm?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/dcc432d5632ebd60cb90f6ed76ac2993.mp4?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The infected do not all think alike – watch out for new weapons and attack patterns. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/6304141993a42987bb567a906fc05fd7.webp?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/1c11177d3f426bb24ccda60fd504d991.poster.avif?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/1c11177d3f426bb24ccda60fd504d991.webm?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/1c11177d3f426bb24ccda60fd504d991.mp4?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your weapons are limited – use them well. Balance item durability against increasingly difficult enemies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/9d00754ef2edc72c01bf0bfb985f92b7.webp?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/105effb5ebb2eb8a166ed714df435c48.poster.avif?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/105effb5ebb2eb8a166ed714df435c48.webm?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/105effb5ebb2eb8a166ed714df435c48.mp4?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play a game of cat and mouse in the shadows. Stay cautious – the infected can hear your footsteps! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/18e0f41ac4f19d26b4e03ac825ec809a.webp?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/3f9350e1159dec69b7fc3b1486dc038e.poster.avif?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/3f9350e1159dec69b7fc3b1486dc038e.webm?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/3f9350e1159dec69b7fc3b1486dc038e.mp4?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>What is this mysterious gas, and who unleashed it? Unravel the global conspiracy with each new chapter. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/a2cb5f0c7de6f22c68ae84fc42dc7433.webp?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/08946a763e99a194d481739b2ec596ed.poster.avif?t=1716290583\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/08946a763e99a194d481739b2ec596ed.webm?t=1716290583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289780/extras/08946a763e99a194d4